1986;;The Patriot;;American;;Frank Harris;;Gregg Henry, Simone Griffeth, Michael J. Pollard;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Patriot_(1986_film);;A gang lead by a man called Atkins (played by Stack Pierce) steal nuclear weapons from a storage facility in the desert.[1] A burnt out former Navy SEAL and Vietnam vet who was previously dishonorably discharged, he is contacted by his former commanding officer to help retrieve the weapons.[2][3][4]